This is the 7th day I can't send messages and this is the problem you're stopping me from handling.

I need to send this message to a group member but I can't because you haven't lifted the block on my message ability. She has violated the group rules and has been removed and blocked, but I can't even tell her that.

You have been removed from and blocked from Resources for posting the advertising for digitizing services. This is a blatant violation of the group rules you should have read before applying to join. You will not be allowed back in the group without contacting the owner, Lenora Porzillo, after two weeks.
